Wilson Audio is an American high-end audio loudspeaker manufacturing company, located in Provo, Utah. Founded by David Wilson and Sheryl Lee Wilson in 1973. David Wilson is currently Wilson Audio's Chairman of the Board and Sheryl Lee Wilson serves as Vice Chair. The daily operations at Wilson Audio are currently directed and managed by Dave Wilson's son and successor CEO Daryl C. Wilson along with COO Korbin Vaughn. David Wilson continues to work closely with Wilson Audio's R&D and Engineering team in product development.
